OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start in the east then
OL,6,Fa dry day with plenty of sunshine
OL,7,Fdeveloping. Feeling quite warm in the
OL,8,Fafternoon, especially in the west, but
OL,9,Fcooler along the east coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA bright end to the day then
OL,12,Fa dry night with long clear spells.
OL,13,FBecoming chilly overnight with patchy
OL,14,Ffog and frost developing.
OL,15,
OL,16,CFriday:FAny patchy fog will soon clear
OL,17,Fthen another dry day with long periods
OL,18,Fof sunshine. Becoming warm inland by
OL,19,Fthe afternoon but cooler near the
OL,20,Fcoast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
